Prevent TypeError in case Server requests unsupported authentication.

If the SOCKS5 server requests username/pasword authentication and
if we do not have username/password, raise SOCKS5AuthError instead of
TypeError.

returns - when connected
adds connect_ex method just like the original socket module
Remove support for EOL Python 3.3
